layout: base.njk
---
{% include 'sitenav.njk' %}

<main>
  <div class="narrative">
    <section class="home-intro">
      <h1>We make things worth listening to.</h1>

      <p>Unstyled is a small UK studio. We produce podcasts, build communities, and ship side projects — mostly late at night, occasionally at weekends.</p>

      <p>Si Jobling has been doing this since 2003. Two decades of making things on the internet.</p>

      {% storyCard "stat", "20+", "years of making things online" %}

      <p>You'll find podcasts for creative technologists, conversations about engineering leadership, and tools that scratch a particular itch. There's also a calendar for rugby fans who refuse to miss a match.</p>

      <p>No sidebars. No noise. Just the work.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="home-projects">
      <h2>The work</h2>
      <ul class="projects-list" role="list">
        {%- for project in collections.projects -%}
        <li class="projects-list__item">
          <a class="projects-list__link" href="{{ project.data.url or project.url }}">{{ project.data.title }}</a>
          <p class="projects-list__desc">{{ project.data.description }}</p>
        </li>
        {%- endfor -%}
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>
</main>
